deranged baby with a weapon.

07:23.400 --> 07:26.035
Such a waste of money and glitter.

07:26.069 --> 07:28.137
Oh, I didn't realize you
were so fond of glitter.

07:28.172 --> 07:30.139
Last year I spent three weeks engraving

07:30.174 --> 07:32.909
a leather banjo strap with
my girlfriend's initials

07:32.943 --> 07:35.178
and sunflowers on it. As
I'm driving up to her house,

07:35.212 --> 07:38.982
I get a text that says, "sorry, but
I'm just not feeling it anymore."

07:39.016 --> 07:40.384
Sometimes I really hate phones.

07:40.418 --> 07:43.287
Yeah well, now I just
put my angst into acting.

07:45.089 --> 07:46.990
Wait, you're doing the play too?

07:47.025 --> 07:49.159
Mm-hmm. I saw you were doing it,

07:49.193 --> 07:52.129
