07:52.163 --> 07:53.997
and now I'm Romeo.

07:54.032 --> 07:55.933
What? Wherefore art thou, dude?

07:55.967 --> 07:57.001
I know. It's crazy.

07:57.035 --> 07:59.070
I think there were four hearing guys

07:59.104 --> 08:00.271
and five speaking parts.

08:00.305 --> 08:02.873
So they were a little desperate, obviously.

08:02.908 --> 08:05.175
Don't forget me when you're
the next James Franco.

08:05.210 --> 08:08.212
